6.The flight_id,departure_date,departure_location and destination of flights departing after
  2024-02-06 sort the result by departure time in asending order ?
  ans: select flight_id,DEPARTURE_DATE,DEPARTURE_LOCATION,DESTINATION from flight
 where DEPARTURE_DATE >'2024-02-06'
 order by DEPARTURE_TIME asc

